Parliament, Tuesday, 02 July 2019 – The Portfolio Committee on Public Enterprises will tomorrow be briefed by the Department of Public Enterprises on its annual performance plan and budget for 2019/20 financial year. Details of the meeting:
	Date: Wednesday, 03 July 2019
	Time: 09:30
